  "summary": {
    "en": "A 158-piece fort kit with storage bag for larger secret bases, arched frames, and multi-child play.",
    "zh": "158件带收纳袋堡垒拼搭套装，适合更大的秘密基地、拱形框架和多人玩耍。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 158-piece configuration gives children more parts for wider forts, rounded frames, and imaginative play structures.",
      "Durable PP rods and connector balls are suitable for repeated assembly, take-down, and storage.",
      "The included storage bag improves organization for families, classrooms, and mobile activity programs.",
      "The product is suitable for retail, education channels, gift projects, and OEM/ODM customization."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "158件配置提供更多组件，可搭建更宽的堡垒、圆角框架和想象力游戏结构。",
      "耐用PP杆件和连接球适合反复拼装、拆卸和收纳。",
      "配套收纳袋方便家庭、课堂和移动活动项目整理。",
      "产品适合零售、教育渠道、礼品项目和OEM/ODM定制。"
    ]
  },
